Package com.ibm.portal.ibmportlet.service.model Description

This package defines ways to obtain models from within an IBM-conform portlet.

Please see the package com.ibm.portal.model for details.

The IBM portlet API is deprecated since 6.0. Support of the IBM portlet API may be removed in a future release of WebSphere Portal. Use of the Java Portlet API (javax.portlet) is recommended instead.

The appropriate services for these portlets are located in com.ibm.portal.portlet.service.model.
